{"tid":795272,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱重睇返天子尋龍, 碧瑤仙子真係好正","createTime":"2018-08-27T01:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T05:57:15.000Z","uid":37288,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f01a891068801608428b7f6a2daaddf3cc0818","tid":795272,"uid":37288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:17:33.000Z","msg":"link: <a href=\"http://8maple.ru/tag/天子尋龍%2F大唐龍珠線上看/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F8maple.ru%2Ftag%2F%E5%A4%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%8B%E9%BE%8D%252F%E5%A4%A7%E5%94%90%E9%BE%8D%E7%8F%A0%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E7%9C%8B%2F&d=ZGIDNEE%2FQoc1KCe8%2F31F0E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=99dbde12\" target=\"_blank\">http://8maple.ru/tag/天子尋龍%2F大唐龍珠線上看/</a><br />\n<br />\n第4集變咗普通話, 想追返原版可以上bilibili<br />\n<br />\n文頌嫻做碧瑤仙子做得好靚好可愛。好記得佢輕飄飄比風吹走阿二攬實佢唔放果幕, 仲有啲嬲樣都係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜依家無keep, 唔係嘅話有第2季揾返佢做都想睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/091609_ac64eb5e2596993cfc34dbf7757123cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F091609_ac64eb5e2596993cfc34dbf7757123cd.png&h=54b985cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/091635_acd4726fddb44a0b565349c078d5b170.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F091635_acd4726fddb44a0b565349c078d5b170.png&h=aa6cfaa6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58dd247132d46f62ba2163cea06e91259e22e356","tid":795272,"uid":37288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:30:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rAk771hgZIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrAk771hgZIs&d=ZGIDNEE%2FQoc1KCe8%2F31F0E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=91ad4229\" ta